item.title: About
item.description: Hello! My name is Natasha, and this is a personal blog that I use to keep record of any projects or knowledge relating to my studies in the IT and cyber security fields that I undertake throughout the course of my university degree, or in my personal time. I will use this blog to learn new concepts and practices in the IT and cyber security field, and then work to explain these concepts in a way that is simple and easy to understand for a non-technical oriented audience.
